segmentosSRT.text: Red Guards are swarming over the place.
segmentosSRT.speaker: SPEAKER_07

segmentosSRT.text:
I just caught them on a ladder,
pulling off roof tiles.
segmentosSRT.speaker: SPEAKER_07

segmentosSRT.text: No idea! The leader is a cripple.
segmentosSRT.speaker: SPEAKER_07

segmentosSRT.text: You've gone to so much trouble.
segmentosSRT.speaker: SPEAKER_07

segmentosSRT.text: What do you think about Fengxia and me?
segmentosSRT.speaker: SPEAKER_07

segmentosSRT.text: We've been through the valley of death.
segmentosSRT.speaker: SPEAKER_07
